2009-05-17  Saturnino Luz  <luzs@cs.tcd.ie>

	* modnlp/tc/util/MakeTermByDocMatrix.java: added utility to create
	term x doc matrices in CSV or ARFF formats

2007-08-17  S. Luz  <luzs@cs.tcd.ie>

	* TCProbabilityModel.java, BVProbabilityModel.java: Fixed bugs,
	moved some general stuff brom BVProbabilityModel up to
	TCProbabilityModel; renamed package modnlp-tc; added option for
	Laplace smoothing;

2006-07-30  Saturnino Luz  <luzs@acm.org>

	Revamped modnlp and implemented better integration between
	modnlp-tc and the nlp suite. Replaced modnlp.tc.parser.Tokenizer by
	basic tokeniser modnlp.util.Tokeniser (moved from
	modnlp.idx.inverted); moved a few general classes from
	modnlp.tc.util into modnlp.util and did the same for
	modnlp.tc.dstruct (into modnlp.dstruct).  
	
2005-05-17  Saturnino Luz  <luzs@acm.org>

	Initial release.

	
